   <body>
      <p>The <uicontrol>DATA OPERATIONS</uicontrol> block  enables you to read, insert, or update information from any form in <ph href="../../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/>. You can configure <uicontrol>SELECT</uicontrol>, <uicontrol>INSERT</uicontrol>, or <uicontrol>UPDATE</uicontrol> queries using blocks by specifying from where the information must be retrieved and the destination to which the information must be  updated or inserted.</p>
      <p>The <uicontrol>DATA OPERATIONS</uicontrol> block has three types of entities:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <xref href="Get_Block.xml">Get</xref>
         </li>
         <li>
            <xref href="Read_Data.xml">Read Data</xref>
         </li>
         <li>
            <xref href="Fields.xml">Fields</xref>
         </li>
      </ul>
